<h2>Drag and Drop</h2>
<p>Drag the box back and forth between the two div elements.</p>

<div id="div1" style="float: left; width: 100px; height: 35px; margin: 10px; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid black;" ondrop="drop(event)" ondragover="allowDrop(event)"></div>

<div id="div2" style="float: left; width: 100px; height: 35px; margin: 10px; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid black;" ondrop="drop(event)" ondragover="allowDrop(event)"></div>

<div id="drag1" draggable="true" ondragstart="drag(event)" style="width: 50px; height: 50px; background-color: #ccc;"></div>

<div id="drag2" draggable="true" ondragstart="drag(event)" style="width: 50px; height: 50px; background-color: #ccc;"></div>
